nielsenCbetSettings.description: Used to insert watermarks of type Nielsen CBET. See Nielsen CBET Settings for more details.

nielsenDistributionType.description: Distribution types to assign to the watermarks. Options are `PROGRAM_CONTENT` and `FINAL_DISTRIBUTOR`.

nielsenNaesIiNwSettings.description: Used to insert watermarks of type Nielsen NAES, II (N2) and Nielsen NAES VI (NW). See Nielsen NAES II NW Settings for more details.
